item.description: In early March 2012, judoka from the Imperial College Judo club arriving for what was otherwise another regular evening of hard judo practice at ETHOS, found themselves very unexpectedly honoured by a visit from the Olympic Champion (Athens 2004) and World Championship judo gold medallist (Brazil â€¦
